I found this on a hotel site and it was a great value for the money.	I booked online and was quoted a very good price.	This Best Western was an excellent value and one of the better priced hotels in the area.	We picked this hotel based on a cheap price we were able to get on Priceline.com and on the TripAdvisor rating.	For the price it seemed a very good deal indeed.	I would not hesitate to stay here again, This is a fairly basic hotel with a few extras, and excellent value that we found unbeatable.